5:
Idol group Franchouchou here!
Come see what we're all about!
8:
They're holding their first concert
soon! Please come check it out!
11:
Phew... With all the flyers we handed
out, I'm expecting a decent
audience.
15: Yes, I believe it will be quite an event.
22:
Um... Are you sure this is the right
timing for a concert?
27:
There've been rumors that monsters
have been popping up after weird
earthquakes lately. A concert could
be risky...
31:
Oh, I had no idea! Hm, what should
we do...
36:
No worries. We'll be acting as event
security the whole time. Right, Stella?
42: Yes, we will safeguard the venue.
47:
Why are you going out of your way
for us? It's not like we can give
anything back in return.
50:
The promise of being able to see
your concert is a reward in itself.
52: So please go through with it.
57:
Stella... Thank you so much! I won't
let you down!
63:
You just leave any monsters to us.
We'll make sure this concert goes
smoothly!
67:
I press this switch when they've
gone onstage. And I press this one
when the first song begins...
71:
I'm sorry to ask for your help with the
lighting. We're short on staff, you
see...
74:
Worry not, for I do not mind in the
least. The switch for the second
song is... this one? No, it should be
this one!
81: Wow! Get a load of the crowds!
86:
This isn't our first concert ever, but
it's been so long since our last one...
I'm kinda nervous!
90:
But it is our first concert in this new
Saga... It's going to be a challenge.
96:
Nothing to be afraid of, Shrimpy!
We've just gotta power through it
now that we've made it all the way
here.
100:
Yeah, all that's left is to make this
the best concert we possibly can.
105: Can we get a final comment, Sakura?
110:
This is our first show since waking up
in this world, but... Stella, our first fan
here, will be watching us.
113:
We owe it to her and all the other
fans to completely blow them away!
117: Yeah! Let's show 'em what we've got!
125:
What's with the glowing sticks? Are
these things supposed to be
weapons?
129:
Ahaha, not exactly. We're supposed
to swing them around. It even
changes color if you press here.
141:
Look how brilliantly they shine!
They're amazing!
144:
Nice... They're definitely the real deal
as idols.
149:
We're Franchouchou, and we
appreciate you all coming out to
our first concert in Saga!
151:
We idols are gonna dominate the
world starting right here! You're
about to witness history!
157:
Don't tell me... Was that one of the
new monsters in town?
171:
What happened to you, Romero?!
Had a little too much to eat?!
176:
This is bad! We should cut the
concert short—
183:
I'm sure Romero's just gotten a bit
chunky from the stress of not
getting enough playtime!
188:
How do you even come up with
such logical fallacies?!
193:
C'mon, girls! Shower Romero with a
bit of attention, would you?
197:
I have no idea what's going on, but
the show must go on! Saki—MC
duties, if you will!
201:
Would you look at that?! A giant fan
of ours is here to watch! On to the
next song!
213:
Eep, Romero! You're not supposed to
be onstage!
217:
We can't ignore it any longer! Let's
fight the dog off—
221:
Wait, don't hurt Romero! He's our
cute little puppy!
225:
Seriously? That big doggo right
there?!
229:
In his normal state, he's really small!
Maybe playing with him a bit will
bring him back to his normal size...
241:
Okay, we're going to draw his
attention while the rest of you focus
on the concert!
245: Got it! You be careful now!
250:
Tch. So we've gotta buy 'em time by
fending off an overgrown mutt, eh?
254:
Won't be your first time holding
back, Nimbus.
262:
Let's go! The success of
Franchouchou's first performance is
riding on us!
